{#- LLM-facing text is English-only: Cyrillic uses roughly 2–3× more tokens per word.
    This Jinja comment is stripped and never sent to the model.
    User prompt for response_observe LLM summarization.
    Variables: is_empty (bool), live_count (int), total_chars (int),
              chunks (list of {position: int, content: str|None, deleted: bool}),
              deleted_positions (list of int). -#}
{% if is_empty -%}
The response buffer is empty. No chunks have been appended yet.
{%- else -%}
Response buffer: {{ live_count }} live chunks, ~{{ total_chars }} chars total.
{% if deleted_positions %}Deleted positions: {{ deleted_positions | join(", ") }}.{% endif %}

{% for chunk in chunks -%}
{% if not chunk.deleted -%}
--- [{{ chunk.position }}] ({{ chunk.content | length }} chars) ---
{{ chunk.content }}

{% endif -%}
{% endfor -%}
{%- endif %}
